Package civitas.celestis.util

Class Triple<E>

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.util.Triple<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of element this tuple should hold
All Implemented Interfaces:
Tuple<E>, Serializable, Iterable<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Triple.TriTriple
public class Triple<E> extends Object implements Tuple<E>
A fixed-size tuple which can only hold three elements. Triples use ABC notation to identity their elements.
